{
  "title": "Mildly Spicy Jamaican Chicken Skewers",
  "description": "A citrusy and comforting Jamaican dish featuring horseradish and grilled to perfection on binchotan charcoal, this recipe is diabetic-friendly and perfect for a weeknight dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Jamaican",
  "diet": [
    "diabetic-friendly",
